thread.title_full: Max Guitar Beoordeeld door Carlos Delgado Villapalos

author: Carlos Delgado Villapalos
title: Carlos Delgado Villapalos
text: Many thanks to Maxguitars, I received the guitar in record time. I have to say that despite being a B-Stock guitar, it is in perfect condition ie totally new. I am very satisfied with the Fender LTD american standard telecaster channel bound dakota red, it is a beautiful guitar with exceptional finishes besides being a very exclusive guitar. Thanks again to Maxguitars.
